main event: A report detailing a sighting of 8 to 10 UFOs over the Pacific Ocean on May 21, 1962.
interesting points: The objects were observed moving in relation to stars,The sighting occurred at 0150 Zulu and lasted approximately one minute,The course of the objects was reported as South South East,The sky was moonlit with six tenths cloud coverage at the time of the sighting,No aircraft contacts were identified on radar during the sighting.
sighted object: 8 to 10 glowing objects in the night sky
witness description: OOD, Boatswain of watch, lookout, and the entire bridge watch.
